description:
Danny updates us on the JLO/Arod/Madison drama, then recaps this week's Summer House, which featured a Powerpoint with aggressive clip art. On The Real Housewives of Atlanta, Cynthia gets married and Porsha sits down with Dennis.


Summer House Recap: 6:01ish

RHOA Recap: 16:17ish
